sentences: Harris is a founding member of the CCM male quartet, 4Him, which toured and recorded from 1990 to 2006.
Harris began a solo career in 2005 and released his debut solo album, The Line Between the Two.
In 2009, he released a Christmas album titled, Christmas Is.
In 2011, he released his fourth solo project, Stronger in the Broken Places.
He also released a book with Howard Publishing/Simon and Schuster in 2009, that bears the same title as his hit, "Find Your Wings".
Harris joined the staff at Gateway Church in Southlake, Texas, in March 2013, and serves as executive pastor of worship ministries.
He won a GMA Dove Award in the category of Inspirational Song of the Year for his single "Find Your Wings".
